Hello there, ProjectFatality is a new gaming community looking for players. Currently, we've got a Garry's Mod server and now we're expanding towards a Runescape private server. This server is still in development and we're still adding things to it. If you'd like to visit the forums go to: [url=http://projectfatality.com/forum/]ProjectFatality - Forums[/url]
We currently have two versions of the client, a downloadable version of the client and a web client.
